Welcome to Benzor Grand Apartments. Various levels of boarding are available to match your means. 

Stable: ( Free) The free city of Benzor provides this resting point for your animals and persons free of charge. 

Common Room: ( 10 Gold Crowns per night ) Thought your pets must stay within the barn for durration of your stay this common room is perfect for a quick nap. 

Private Room: ( 100 Gold Crowns per night ) Enjoy a restful night sleep or reverie that only solitude can bring. 

Luxury Suite: ( 1000 Gold Crowns per night ) Lack nothing while you relax within the lap of luxury.

Entering Sleeping area. In consideration for others please keep your voice to a whisper.

Merchant Tills
In Nordock Rogue and Bard characters may attempt to use Slight of Hand to steal a few coins from a vendor's purse. Simply click on this object and follow the conversation. However no reward comes without risk so note that there is a small chance of getting caught each time you try and as an illegal act if caught you face potential jail time from the guards. But a canny escape artist should be out in no time. Characters wishing to become more proficient at this should train in picking pockets. Success can only be met at each till once per reset and if discovered you cannot attempt on the same till again that reset.
